27	/**
28	 * POST /api/admin/create-indexes
29	 *
30	 * Creates MongoDB indexes across all major collections to improve query
31	 * performance. Safe to re-run — MongoDB skips indexes that already exist.
32	 * Restricted to admin and developer roles. Returns a per-collection status
33	 * report listing successes and any errors encountered.
