3	 *
4	 * Administrative endpoint to synchronize SMIB classification status for all locations.
5	 * Classifies each location based on its machines' relayId presence:
6	 * - fullSMIBs: all machines have relayId
7	 * - semiSMIBs: some machines have relayId
8	 * - noSMIBLocation: no machines have relayId
