75	/**
76	 * POST /api/admin/smib-sync
77	 *
78	 * Triggers a full SMIB classification sync for all accessible locations.
79	 * Can optionally filter by licencee.
80	 * Restricted to admin/developer roles.
81	 *
82	 * Body fields:
